title: ranked season confusion?
body: I just got a message about ranked starting today. what's going on?

replies.body: Straaaaange. I wonder if for some reason you're just now seeing that notification from back in December. The current ranked season has been going on since [**Dec 7**](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/competitive/2017-ranked-season-kicks).

http://i.imgur.com/hxMQrfW.png

third time it's happened now.
